query:
INSERT INTO deposits (userId, amount, network, depositAddress, txHash, status, adminNotes, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT userId, amount, 'Migration' as network, 'migrated' as depositAddress, CONCAT('migration-', id) as txHash, 'confirmed' as status, notes as adminNotes, createdAt, updatedAt
FROM pointTransactions 
WHERE type = 'credit' 
AND id NOT IN (SELECT CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(txHash, '-', -1) AS UNSIGNED) FROM deposits WHERE network = 'Migration');
